&quot; means 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“imitating”">&quot;imitating&quot;</normalizedToken>
and refers to the morphological similarities of the new species and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Lam" authorityYear="1797" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Corbichoniaceae" genus="Mollugo" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Mollugo nudicaulis" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="8" pageNumber="101" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="nudicaulis">
